### **5.1 ATOMIC TRANSACTION BOUNDARIES**

**ENGINEERING REQUIREMENT**: All inventory operations must be atomic

**IMPLEMENTATION PATTERN**:
```php
DB::beginTransaction();
try {
    // 1. Lock all affected records
    // 2. Perform validations
    // 3. Execute updates
    // 4. Verify consistency
    // 5. Log changes
    DB::commit();
} catch (Exception $e) {
